      "raw_text": "there has ben any loss of interest\nin the cleanup movement.\n\n\nMr.. Martin has recently been d.\nviding his time between picking\nstrawberries, preaching the gospel\nand talking woman suffrage. With\nall of these cares he has not over\nlooked the fact that If the farmers\nare to get the benefit of their year\nand a half's work for better govern\nment they must unite and act in\nthe coming county primaries."
